  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the ginger and garlic and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Add the ground beef and stir-fry until browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "Add the beef stock, salt, black pepper, turmeric, cumin, and paprika. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lime juice, rice vinegar, and cilantro. Cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
